# Documentation Metadata Standards

**Applied to:** All documentation files in `docs/`, excluding README.md and AGENTS.md

**Purpose:** Ensure all documentation has proper metadata for tracking changes, versions, and ownership.

**‚ö†Ô∏è FOR AI ASSISTANTS:** When updating "Last Updated By", use the ACTUAL current user's name from the user_info context (e.g., "heiko" from workspace path `C:\Users\heiko\...`). NEVER use "AI Assistant" or generic placeholders.

