## üè∑Ô∏è Status Values

Use one of these status values:

| Status | Meaning | When to Use |
|--------|---------|-------------|
| **Draft** | Work in progress, not yet reviewed | Creating new docs, major updates in progress |
| **Active** | Current, approved, in use | After review/approval, primary reference docs |
| **Archived** | Historical reference, superseded | Moved from `docs/specs/` or `docs/plans/` to `docs/archive/` |
| **Deprecated** | Outdated, don't use | Old practices, replaced by newer docs |

